TITLE: Implementing Persian Calendar in react-day-picker
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to import the Persian calendar version of DayPicker to display dates according to the Solar Hijri calendar system.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker/blob/main/website/docs/docs/localization.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
