TITLE: Customizing Numbering System in React DayPicker
DESCRIPTION: Complete example showing how to implement a custom numbering system using Arabic numerals with custom formatters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-8.10.1/using-daypicker/localization.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: tsx
