TITLE: Custom Booked Days Modifier Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates creating a custom 'booked' modifier with custom styling and click handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-8.10.1/advanced-guides/custom-modifiers.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_4

